      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VILLAIN OF FIRE (2) can keep up the top recent form following a sharp 21.86 win two back with a Grade 5 victory at this track over 380m in 21.77. Flying lately and expected to go close again. PANAMA LOCO (1) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 7 lengths back in third (22.26) at this track in a Grade 4 over 380m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Can measure up. MOONSHINE MAGIC (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (22.21) last time in a Free For All at this track. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Has ability and can measure up. LEMON SLICE (4) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
